\id JHN - Mayali 
\h John 
\toc3 John 
\toc2 John 
\toc1 Djon 
\mt1 Djon  
\c 3  
\p  
\p
\v 16 God kaben-marne-djareng kubolk-warlahken bulkidj, kabenwong beywurd nuye namakkayken nadjalkudji bulkidj. Nangale nawu kabirriwoybukwon, minj kabirridowen bulkidj, kabirridarrkid munguhy-munguhy.  
\v 17 God bimunkeweng beywurd nuye konda kumwam Minj bimunkeweng bu bendjadmeninj bininj dja minj benduyinj. bu kaben-ngehke birridjalwenh bininj bolk-warlahken.   